    "description": "You are a flame that is about to go out, quickly find the exit before time runs out!<br><br>Each time you die you will <strong>learn more</strong> about wrong paths and possible right ones.<br><br>You really need to run and <strong>decide really fast</strong>, your flame won't last if you're slow in your decisions, but most importantly <strong>don't stop</strong> at all or your time will be even faster!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 30 Progressive Levels<br></li><li> Dark Musics<br></li><li> Quicky gameplay<br></li><li> Chaotic Scenario</li></ul><br>Be sure of your path, one wrong step and your fate is likely to be death!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834550/extras/abf42ab60d0d87d5dbc14358bc50c123.poster.avif?t=1770033718\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834550/extras/abf42ab60d0d87d5dbc14358bc50c123.webm?t=1770033718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834550/extras/abf42ab60d0d87d5dbc14358bc50c123.mp4?t=1770033718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>I told you to be quick!<br><br>If you like <strong>fast and frantic experiences</strong> this is probably the perfect game for you!",
